                     <p> BEREFORD ST. MARTIN (Wilts). <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Stoford</surname>
                        </persName>,
                 son and heir of <persName>
                           <forename>Joan</forename> 
                           <surname>Prikemere</surname>
                        </persName>, 
                 grants to <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Peracourt</surname>
                        </persName> the whole of a messuage in the village of
                 <placeName key="place_1083319">Bereford St. Martin's</placeName>. 
